/user

  • tests the router connection

    GET
    GET 
    /hello
    Sample request
    curl 
    /hello
    curl -X GET "http://visionarchive.io/hello"
    Response 200 OK
    body 
    {
  "message": "hello world"
}

  • Set rating on a item for this user. user id, item id, rating (int: 0, 1, 2, 3, 4 or 5)

    PUT
    PUT 
    /user/15847262227907777000/item/84869928
    Sample request
    headers payload curl 
    /user/15847262227907777000/item/84869928
    content-type: application/json
content-length: 60

    {
  "user": "15847262227907777000",
  "item": "84869928",
  "rating": 2
}
    curl -X PUT -H "content-type: application/json" -H "content-length: 60" -d '{"user":"15847262227907777000","item":"84869928","rating":2}' "http://visionarchive.io/user/15847262227907777000/item/84869928"
    Response 200 OK
    body 
    {
  "__v": 0,
  "user": "15847262227907777000",
  "rating": 2,
  "item": "84869928",
  "_id": "57606f072c2c7d82fd08e601"
}
